g0ETExhgwLD1VZ_qkjHfVvcusel58C&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAll-new-Echo-Buds-2023-Release-True-Wireless-Earbuds%2Fdp%2FB09JVG3TWX%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">亚马逊 Echo Buds</a>整体价值更高，但 Ear Stick 的设计更时尚，透明的外壳可以像口红管一样旋转打开。对于这种风格的耳塞来说，其音频质量非常稳定（并且可以根据需要进行定制），而 AirPods 风格的触摸控制则易于使用。每次充电 6 小时左右，电池续航时间还过得去。请记住，这种类型的设计几乎无法阻挡外界噪音，因此它不适合飞行或拥挤的办公室。</p><h2>苹果航空标签</h2><p><core-commerce id="a8bf8d02852f4d2fa1a0749e448e49f1" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:72;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZ15PBFyMKoCK-eTkyUolU147qP72NYQx9kVJUFsk6f-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MX532AM-A-AirTag%2Fdp%2FB0933BVK6T%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple AirTag</a>在<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:73;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZ15PBFyMKoCK-eTkyUolU147qP72NYQx9kVJUFsk6f-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MX532AM-A-AirTag%2Fdp%2FB0933BVK6T%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">亚马逊</a>和<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Walmart;elmt:;cpos:74;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=3719d8d4-5edd-4817-998a-91f3229e7323&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Walmart&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIzNzE5ZDhkNC01ZWRkLTQ4MTctOTk4YS05MWYzMjI5ZTczMjMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud2FsbWFydC5jb20vaXAvQXBwbGUtQWlyVGFnLzQ3NTYzNDEzMT9zZWxlY3RlZD10cnVlIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkN2M2ZjUxMS05ZmQ2LTQzNGUtYjUwZi00ZTQ1NDk3YmNhYTMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAStLwt6znxz1Bho2WXXUbf6t8BdI1sPAgf-DCtHTQ7by&amp