<![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A woman poses with a balloon of Pokemon character Pikachu at Minatomirai shopping district in Yokohama, near Tokyo, Monday, Aug. 14, 2017. (AP Photo/Shizuo Kambayashi)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Japan Daily Life]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Johnson & Johnson gets FDA approval for heart treatments that don't require X-rays]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>强生公司的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.jnjmedtech.com/en-US"><ins>医疗技术部门</ins></a>的<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.jnj.com/biosense-webster-receives-fda-approval-for-multiple-atrial-fibrillation-ablation-products-to-be-used-in-a-workflow-without-fluoroscopy"><ins>新工作流程获得 FDA 批准</ins></a>，该工作流程将使医疗专业人员更安全地治疗心房颤动，心房颤动会导致心跳不规律，并可能<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/atrial-fibrillation/symptoms-causes/syc-20350624"><ins>导致中风或心力衰竭</ins></a>。强生 MedTech 旗下 Biosense Webster 开发的多种产品获得了 FDA 的“零透视工作流程”许可，这意味着在导管插入过程中将不再需要实时 X 射线成像。医疗专业人员现在可以使用超声波来指导治疗，而不是使用 X 射线插入 Biosense 导管。</p><p>使用更少的 X 射线或透视检查可以降低患者和医疗专业人员的辐射暴露。目前，在专门治疗相关心脏手术的治疗室工作的医生和医务人员往往会<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://pdf.sciencedirectassets.com/781090/1-s2.0-S2772930323X00052/1-s2.0-S2772930323005318/main.pdf?X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEIb%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEaCXVzLWVhc3QtMSJHMEUCIHiy4EcMJSMDfam4qpccciIubvzC5gIZNmQNnyDpNL6zAiEAkcfDkwIKqKNbda8L0DJH%2FqG3hDjwoUjpk7JeyHGUnhYqswUILxAFGgwwNTkwMDM1NDY4NjUiDNOU%2BVJ6fRZGLsdLrCqQBR5ZA%2Fbn%2BIUDPrmikxkj3%2Fcd5ZjfmGsP7isZ0LmWgpGy0UCT728P2fUbPXQqWJ56Ik%2BXK0%2BHXWbLb94jQrbqpkTVSvF8mBKwCQewg37GBbNC8Kj%2BAQnuP62OFdsTsd583HuMqJpOMnT4C3jH7O7%2FstN6tA71mqNslv7XMik9KeR%2BJkp0cYQGikMMngRgg4FqV3QkPLj7PGo9Ifjvh8VkEWT6JJaeRIHtTDbpOZDa37npUp5Sa253oDBzSk9zfsaIFx1QuKnzNKNgl8ZBVVX47aSvXE6ykI44o06g9Yc44KSI1p9ut9bKzRbNtVmmOPjlpYDUOqaxwgT%2Fwt4SYV6LEwxxmJlrim%2BWoICCu2EzhmarCmzTzO4nfH5mmVlSWE5zC7tko5oXhYshQgbb7